This is a Cursor-specific overlay. **Canonical source: [`rules/core/routing.md`](https://github.com/commerce-atoms/agents/blob/main/kit/rules/core/routing.md).**

## Single source of truth

- `app/routes.ts` is the only routing manifest.
- Do not add additional route manifest files.
- Do not add a second routing entrypoint that duplicates routing definitions.

## No filesystem routing

- Do not rely on `app/routes/*` filesystem discovery as the routing source of truth.

## Explicit mapping

- Each URL pattern maps explicitly to a route module file under `app/modules/*`.
- Avoid abstractions that generate, auto-compose, or implicitly register routes.

## Layout nesting

- UI routes are nested under the layout shell route (owned by `app/layout/*`).
- Resource routes (`robots.txt`, `sitemap.xml`, etc.) remain outside layout nesting.
